Interface computesFee

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BOXParcel, FLTParcel, Parcel

    public interface computesFee
    The class computesFee is an interface that is used by the Parcel class. This interface includes abstract computations for the Base Rate, Insurance fee, Destination fee, and the Total fee of the Parcel. The interface also generates a breakdown of the cost of the parcel.
